description:
Carnival Eats - Season 3, Episode 1




Royals and the Red River City

Noah Cappe begins his journey at the Royal Winter Fair in Toronto, Canada, where he tries the The Great Canadian Rosti, and tops it all off with the Massive Marshmallow Crunch. Later, he makes his way down to the State Fair of Louisiana, where the specialties include Lupita's Gorditas and The Five Pounder burger.




Original Air Date: 07-Apr-2015
